SQL_STMT_U.val: select NOTDUE, DUE0130, DUE3160, DUE6190, DUE90PLUS from (select cast(sum(A.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as NOTDUE from :1/INVO A where A.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and A.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 and (days(':3') - days(A.INVO_DUEDATE) <0)) as NOTDUE, (select cast(sum(B.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE0130 from :1/INVO B where B.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and B.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 and (days(':3') - days(B.INVO_DUEDATE) between 0 and 30)) as DUE0130, (select cast(sum(C.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE3160 from :1/INVO C where C.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and C.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 and (days(':3') - days(C.INVO_DUEDATE) between 31 and 60)) as DUE3160, (select cast(sum(D.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE6190 from :1/INVO D where D.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and D.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 and (days(':3') - days(D.INVO_DUEDATE) between 61 and 90)) as DUE6190, (select cast(sum(E.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE90PLUS from :1/INVO E where E.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and E.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 and (days(':3') - days(E.INVO_DUEDATE) > 90)) as DUE90PLUS for fetch only

select PAIDAMOUNTINVDATE_A, PAIDAMOUNTDUEDATE_A, PAIDAMOUNT_A, PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTE_A, PAIDAMOUNTPARTIAL_A, TOTSALNOTES_A, PAIDAMOUNTINVDATE_B, PAIDAMOUNTDUEDATE_B, PAIDAMOUNT_B, PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTE_B, PAIDAMOUNTPARTIAL_B, TOTSALNOTES_B from (select cast(sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTINVDATE) as decimal(15,2)) as PAIDAMOUNTINVDATE_A, cast(sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDUEDATE) as decimal(15,2)) as PAIDAMOUNTDUEDATE_A, cast(sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNT) as decimal(13,2)) as PAIDAMOUNT_A, cast(sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTES) as decimal(13,2)) as PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTE_A, cast(sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTPARTIALPAYM) as decimal(13,2)) as PAIDAMOUNTPARTIAL_A, cast(sum(DCMO_TOTASALESDEBTNOTES-DCMO_TOTASALESCREDNOTES) as decimal(13,2)) as TOTSALNOTES_A from :1/DCMO where DCMO_DEBC_NO = :2 and DCMO_YEAR = :3 and DCMO_CURRENCY = ':5') as THISYEAR, (select cast(sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTINVDATE) as decimal(15,2)) as PAIDAMOUNTINVDATE_B, cast(sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDUEDATE) as decimal(15,2)) as PAIDAMOUNTDUEDATE_B, cast(sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNT) as decimal(13,2)) as PAIDAMOUNT_B, cast(sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTES) as decimal(13,2)) as PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTE_B, cast(sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTPARTIALPAYM) as decimal(13,2)) as PAIDAMOUNTPARTIAL_B, cast(sum(DCMO_TOTASALESDEBTNOTES-DCMO_TOTASALESCREDNOTES) as decimal(13,2)) as TOTSALNOTES_B from :1/DCMO where DCMO_DEBC_NO = :2 and DCMO_YEAR = :4 and DCMO_CURRENCY = ':5') as LASTYEAR for fetch only;

SQL_STMT_U.val: select NOTDUE, DUE0130, DUE3160, DUE6190, DUE90PLUS from (select cast(sum(A.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as NOTDUE from :1/INVO A where A.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and A.INVO_AACTUALI > 0 and (days(':3') - days(A.INVO_DUEDATE) <0)) as NOTDUE, (select cast(sum(B.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE0130 from :1/INVO B where B.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and B.INVO_AACTUALI > 0 and (days(':3') - days(B.INVO_DUEDATE) between 0 and 30)) as DUE0130, (select cast(sum(C.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE3160 from :1/INVO C where C.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and C.INVO_AACTUALI > 0 and (days(':3') - days(C.INVO_DUEDATE) between 31 and 60)) as DUE3160, (select cast(sum(D.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE6190 from :1/INVO D where D.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and D.INVO_AACTUALI > 0 and (days(':3') - days(D.INVO_DUEDATE) between 61 and 90)) as DUE6190, (select cast(sum(E.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE90PLUS from :1/INVO E where E.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and E.INVO_AACTUALI > 0 and (days(':3') - days(E.INVO_DUEDATE) > 90)) as DUE90PLUS for fetch only
select cast(sum(INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/INVO where INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and INVO_AACTUALI < 0 for fetch only

select PAYDAYS_A, SALESYEAR_A, PAYDAYS_B, SALESYEAR_B from (select cast((sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTINVDATE)/sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNT - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTES - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTPARTIALPAYM)) as decimal(13,2)) as PAYDAYS_A, cast(sum(DCMO_TOTASALESDEBTNOTES - DCMO_TOTASALESCREDNOTES) as decimal(13,2)) as SALESYEAR_A from :1/DCMO where DCMO_DEBC_NO = :2 and DCMO_YEAR = :3 and DCMO_CURRENCY = ':5') as THISYEAR, (select cast((sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTINVDATE)/sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNT - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTES - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTPARTIALPAYM)) as decimal(13,2)) as PAYDAYS_B, cast(sum(DCMO_TOTASALESDEBTNOTES - DCMO_TOTASALESCREDNOTES) as decimal(13,2)) as SALESYEAR_B from :1/DCMO where DCMO_DEBC_NO = :2 and DCMO_YEAR = :4 and DCMO_CURRENCY = ':5') as LASTYEAR for fetch only

Reset variables
INVO_AACTUALI > 0 (for NOTDUE, DUE0130, DUE3160, DUE6190, DUE90PLUS)
INVO_AACTUALI < 0 (for NOTCLEARED)
-- Calc total payment days and sales of this and last year

SQL_STMT_U.val: select NOTDUE, DUE0130, DUE3160, DUE6190, DUE90PLUS from (select cast(sum(A.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as NOTDUE from :1/INVO A where A.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and A.INVO_AACTUALI > 0 and (days(':3') - days(A.INVO_DUEDATE) <0)) as NOTDUE, (select cast(sum(B.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE0130 from :1/INVO B where B.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and B.INVO_AACTUALI > 0 and (days(':3') - days(B.INVO_DUEDATE) between 0 and 30)) as DUE0130, (select cast(sum(C.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE3160 from :1/INVO C where C.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and C.INVO_AACTUALI > 0 and (days(':3') - days(C.INVO_DUEDATE) between 31 and 60)) as DUE3160, (select cast(sum(D.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE6190 from :1/INVO D where D.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and D.INVO_AACTUALI > 0 and (days(':3') - days(D.INVO_DUEDATE) between 61 and 90)) as DUE6190, (select cast(sum(E.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) as DUE90PLUS from :1/INVO E where E.INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and E.INVO_AACTUALI > 0 and (days(':3') - days(E.INVO_DUEDATE) > 90)) as DUE90PLUS for fetch only
select cast(sum(INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/INVO where INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and INVO_AACTUALI < 0 for fetch only

select PAYDAYS_A, SALESYEAR_A, PAYDAYS_B, SALESYEAR_B from (select cast((sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTINVDATE)/sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNT - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTES - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTPARTIALPAYM)) as decimal(13,2)) as PAYDAYS_A, cast(sum(DCMO_TOTASALESDEBTNOTES - DCMO_TOTASALESCREDNOTES) as decimal(13,2)) as SALESYEAR_A from :1/DCMO where DCMO_DEBC_NO = :2 and DCMO_YEAR = :3 and DCMO_CURRENCY = ':5') as THISYEAR, (select cast((sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTINVDATE)/sum(DCMO_PAIDAMOUNT - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTES - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTPARTIALPAYM)) as decimal(13,2)) as PAYDAYS_B, cast(sum(DCMO_TOTASALESDEBTNOTES - DCMO_TOTASALESCREDNOTES) as decimal(13,2)) as SALESYEAR_B from :1/DCMO where DCMO_DEBC_NO = :2 and DCMO_YEAR = :4 and DCMO_CURRENCY = ':5') as LASTYEAR for fetch only
